{{vgname|传送门马里奥|en=Mari0}} 是一個[[开源游戏|開放源碼]][[益智游戏|益智]][[平台游戏|平台]]改編[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]，結合了《[[超级马里奥兄弟|超级马里奥兄弟]]》和《[[Portal|Portal]]》的遊戲元素<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5835600/mari0-puts-a-portal-gun-in-super-mario-bros |title=Mari0 Puts a Portal Gun in Super Mario Bros - Kotaku |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2017-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812100830/http://kotaku.com/5835600/mari0-puts-a-portal-gun-in-super-mario-bros |dead-url=no }}</ref>，由Stabyourself.net的莫里斯·蓋岡開發。蓋岡在開發此遊戲前，亦開發過數個改編遊戲，包括《Not Tetris》（改編自《[[俄羅斯方塊|俄羅斯方塊]]》）。《Mari0》使用的遊戲引擎為LÖVE引擎<ref name="releasedateconfirm">{{Cite web |url=http://www.ubuntuvibes.com/2012/02/mari0-gets-release-date-super-mario.html |title=Mari0 Gets a Release Date  - UbuntuVibes |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2020-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119174729/https://www.ubuntuvibes.com/2012/02/mari0-gets-release-date-super-mario.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，能夠跨平台遊玩，包括[[Linux|Linux]]、[[Mac_OS_X|Mac OS X]]和[[Windows|Windows]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://lalasercenter.zendesk.com/entries/25095754-mari0-Mario-with-Portals-Windows-OSX-Linux-Source |title=mari0 - Mario with Portals! - Windows, OSX, Linux, Source |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2014-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226072034/http://lalasercenter.zendesk.com/entries/25095754-mari0-Mario-with-Portals-Windows-OSX-Linux-Source |dead-url=no }}</ref>此遊戲於2012年3月3日以[[创作共用授权|创作共用授权]]正式發佈。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://github.com/nevyn/mari0 |title=nevyn/mari0 · GitHub |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927005333/https://github.com/nevyn/mari0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>自發佈後，所有人都可以瀏覽遊戲的源代碼。<ref name="officialinformation">{{Cite web |url=http://stabyourself.net/mari0/information/ |title=Mari0 Information - Official Website |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2017-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227032302/http://stabyourself.net/mari0/information |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 遊戲內容 ==

《Mari0》的遊戲界面基本上與8位元版本的2D平台游戏《[[超级马里奥兄弟|超级马里奥兄弟]]》相同。玩家在遊戲中需要使用鍵盤操控[[马力欧_(角色)|马力欧]]走路和跳躍，並需要避開敵人或踩在敵人的頭上。玩家亦需要收集金幣以獲得額外的分數。而與原作最大分別的地方，就是遊戲加入了源自解謎遊戲《[[傳送門|傳送門]]》的「傳送門槍」概念。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://download.cnet.com/Mari0/3000-7433_4-75714261.html |title=Mari0 - Free download and software reviews - CNET Download.com |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2018-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180413152747/http://download.cnet.com/Mari0/3000-7433_4-75714261.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在《Mari0》中，玩家可以在兩個不同平面上用鼠標點擊，即可產生一個傳送門。玩家可以利用傳送門的特性以到達某些地方，如玩家躍下位於地面的傳送門時，自由落體的向下矢量在穿地面越傳送門，並從垂直的傳送門出來後，會轉變為向前的直線衝量，使玩家能到達原本沒辦法抵達的地方。<ref name="commentary">Valve Corporation. (In-game developer commentary) ''Portal''. 2007.</ref>但是，這個效果亦會在敵人身上產生。<ref name="University Observer">{{Cite web |url=http://www.universityobserver.ie/2013/04/04/review-mari0/ |title=Review: Mari0 - University Observer |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2015-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150105040135/http://www.universityobserver.ie/2013/04/04/review-mari0/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

此遊戲的畫面設計與《超级马里奥兄弟》相似，但遊戲中的試驗室則是取材自《傳送門》的光圈科學實驗室。除此之外，此遊戲的[[关卡编辑器|关卡编辑器]]中的圖形編輯器和[[着色器|着色器]]均能讓玩家創造出全新的關卡。但是，此遊戲要到之後的版本才支援多人遊戲。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.indiegamemag.com/mari0-released/ |title=Get Your Portal On With The Release Of ‘Mari0′ - The Indie Game Magazine |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2014-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228144409/http://www.indiegamemag.com/mari0-released/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
起初，Stabyourself.net的首席程序員蓋岡想製作一個包含《[[新_超級瑪利歐兄弟_Wii|新 超級瑪利歐兄弟 Wii]]》多人遊戲獨有元素的《超级马里奥兄弟》改編遊戲。但是，當他在{{tsl|en|CollegeHumor|}}看見了一個名為「持有傳送門槍的馬里奧」的影片後，他便決定加入傳送門槍元素。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://obsoletegamer.com/the-interview-mari0/ |title=The Interview: Mario - Obsolete Gamer |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2012-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120307233913/http://obsoletegamer.com/the-interview-mari0/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dorkly.com/video/14583/dorkly-bits-mario-with-a-portal-gun |title=Dorkly Bits: Mario With A Portal Gun - Dorkly |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2012-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311020556/http://www.dorkly.com/video/14583/dorkly-bits-mario-with-a-portal-gun |dead-url=no }}</ref>

蓋岡於2011年1月開始開發此遊戲。在開發遊戲期間，他頻繁地更新其博客內容，以讓支持者能獲得最新的《Mari0》開發進度資訊，其中包括長達1個月的馬拉松式屏幕截圖更新。蓋岡亦發佈了幾套预告片和視頻，並宣佈此遊戲將於2011年的聖誕節期間面世。後來，蓋岡將發佈時間推延至2011年除夕。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/14612418000/no-christmas-release |title=- Stabyourself.net Stabyourself.net news archive - No Christmas release! :(  |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2012-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328012547/http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/14612418000/no-christmas-release |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，發布日期再進一步被推延，直至beta版的測試已經完成，以及蓋岡對遊戲感到滿意為止。

最終，蓋岡以謎題的形式宣佈發布日期，而發布日期就是2012年3月3日。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ubuntuvibes.com/2012/02/mari0-gets-release-date-super-mario.html |title=Mari0 Gets a Release Date Super Mario Bros Meets Portal - UBUNTU VIBES |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2020-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119174729/https://www.ubuntuvibes.com/2012/02/mari0-gets-release-date-super-mario.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/17384294401/its-a-riddle |title=- Stabyourself.net Stabyourself.net news archive - It's a riddle |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2012-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120428185516/http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/17384294401/its-a-riddle |dead-url=no }}</ref>Stabyourself.net亦在其首頁上加上了一個倒計時器，以告訴支持者距離發佈日期尚有多久。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/18397781826/countdown |title=- Stabyourself.net Stabyourself.net news archive - Countdown! |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2012-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427211510/http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/18397781826/countdown |dead-url=no }}</ref>

首個官方版本是伴隨著一個預告片一起發布的。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/18685852715/mari0-released |title=- Stabyourself.net Stabyourself.net news archive - Mari0 RELEASED!! |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2012-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120424201718/http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/18685852715/mari0-released |dead-url=no }}</ref>除此之外，Stabyourself.net亦會不時發佈遊戲補丁版本。<ref name="mari016">{{Cite web |url=http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/19416523191/mari0-1-6-riot-shield-famas-and-galil |title=- Stabyourself.net Mari0 1.6! Riot shield, famas and galil |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2012-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120321022926/http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/19416523191/mari0-1-6-riot-shield-famas-and-galil |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/18728000184/update-1-1 |title=- Stabyourself.net Stabyourself.net news archive - Update 1.1 |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302032005/http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/18728000184/update-1-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/18752093583/update-1-2-third-times-a-charm |title=- Stabyourself.net Stabyourself.net news archive - Update 1.2! Third time's a charm |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302030331/http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/18752093583/update-1-2-third-times-a-charm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/18872999480/mari0-1-3-the-biggest-update-yet |title=- Stabyourself.net Stabyourself.net news archive - Mari0 1.3: The biggest update yet |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302024929/http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/18872999480/mari0-1-3-the-biggest-update-yet |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.stabyourself.net/post/18955905309/mari0-1-4-it-will-never-