== 評價 ==
《Mari0》在發佈後即獲得多個技術和電子遊戲網站的關注。此遊戲亦獲得很多知名網站的關注，如[[YouTube|YouTube]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WtcGiZelPfk |title=Mari0 on YouTube |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023063226/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WtcGiZelPfk |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[Reddit|Reddit]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reddit.com/r/gaming/comments/qe1o3/sheer_awesomeness_xpost_from_rgifs/ |title=Mari0 on reddit |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2016-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160713184903/https://www.reddit.com/r/gaming/comments/qe1o3/sheer_awesomeness_xpost_from_rgifs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>此遊戲獲得的評價大多是正面的。[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]的約翰·沃克指出「如果它（《Mari0》）沒有令到你喘氣，並令你希望將它張貼到互聯網的其餘部分的話，那麼我根本不明白你。」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2011/10/17/prepare-to-want-mari0-is-remarkable/ |title=Prepare To Want: Mari0 Is Remarkable - Rock, Paper, Shotgun |accessdate=2014-02-22 |archive-date=2012-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120212202117/http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2011/10/17/prepare-to-want-mari0-is-remarkable/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

